cs.LG, cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper deals with optimizing energy consumption on mobile platforms for CNN computations, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of cloud computing for offloading computations also falls under the category of distributed systems (cs.DC) and networking (cs.NI). The formulation of an analytical energy model for deep learning accelerators is related to control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.NE).
